  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening access to rights on social security schemes for the marginalized</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Orientation to the project team and enumerator on data collection from 20000 HH from Odisha, MP, UP, Rajasthan , Delhi/NCR who have not received the entitlements. Second round We Claim App developed to track exclusion and enable inclusion into social security schemes. 60% of the 20000 HH to file applications for social security schemes. Survey data analysed for advocacy actions. State &amp; National level consultation with partners and stakeholders. To engage with authorities on follow up of applications. Launching on line campaigns for awareness on Covid impact to marginalised communities.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through data collection to ensure 60% of 20000 HH to file applications to access social welfare schemes and enable them to enrol will ensure realization of benefits.</narrative>
  </description>
